  "prompt": "What is Zooey Deschanel's relationship like with her sister Emily?",
  "response": "Zooey Deschanel and her sister Emily Deschanel have a close and supportive relationship. Both sisters are actresses, known for their roles in popular TV shows and movies. Zooey starred in \"New Girl,\" while Emily is known for her role in \"Bones.\" \n\nThey often express their admiration and support for each other in public. For instance, they have attended events together and shared posts on social media celebrating each other's achievements. They also share a common interest in music and have collaborated on projects, such as appearing in a music video together for the band She & Him, in which Zooey is a vocalist.\n\nTheir bond extends to their family life as well; they have been seen spending time with their children and other family members, showcasing a tight-knit family unit. Overall, Zooey and Emily Deschanel share a warm, loving, and supportive sisterly relationship.",
